text: Phaenomenella cirsiumoides is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks.Bouchet, P. (2014). Phaenomenella cirsiumoides (Fraussen, 2004). Accessed through: World Register of Marine Species at http://www.marinespecies.org/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id;=703939 on 2014-09-27 ==Description== ==Distribution== This species occurs in the South China Sea. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Buccinidae Category:Gastropods described in 2004
title: Phaenomenella cirsiumoides
